snippet.textDisplay:
Lets discuss about the message in the song given by Mann sahib.. 

1. One line that has given gooseBumps to lakhs of Punjabi hearts in India & Pak is:

RAAVI TO CHENAB PUSHDA..... KI HAAL HAI SATLUJ DA...

I think although punjabis on both sides have laid down their lives in war, but Still their hearts want to sing the song of Peace and Harmony.. I hope One day both countries would unite in name of their ancestory and history.

Mel tu Karaade Rabba, Dilli te Lahore da..

2. The Kind of influence Movies and Songs have had on our Morality in day to day life and especially, on conjugal (Love) matters is depressing, as this songs depicts.

Its uncool to protect one's dignity before marriage, be it a guy or gal. In name of freedom, both sexes are shaming prides of their elders, when they meet in private places secretly to indulge in sexual affairs.

Why are 999 out of 1000 songs based on  "Mainu tu Shadd gayi", "Goliyaa, bandukaa", "Peg, Kudi" ?? Songs do influence our lifestyles and social fabric.

Here, Mann sahib is a Jewel.. Never sung a Vulgar Song, but Still biggest star of Punjabi..

Gustakhi maaf..
